# Hotel ERP API Examples
# Use this file to test API endpoints
# Requires a REST client like VS Code REST Client extension or Postman

### Variables
@host = http://localhost:9000
@apiBase = {{host}}/api
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Documentation Health
GET {{host}}/docs/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Authentication - Login
POST {{apiBase}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password123"
}

### POS - Create Sale
POST {{apiBase}}/pos/sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 25.99
    },
    {
      "item_id": 2,
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 15.50
    }
  ],
  "discount": 10.5,
  "tax_rate": 8.25
}

### POS - Get Sales History (Basic)
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### POS - Get Sales History (With Filters)
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?page=1&limit=10&start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

