### Pagination Examples

### First Page
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Second Page
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Large Page Size
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?page=1&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Date Range Examples

### Current Month
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Last Week
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?start_date=2024-01-08&end_date=2024-01-15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Today Only
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?start_date=2024-01-15&end_date=2024-01-15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Combined Filters
GET {{apiBase}}/pos/sales/history?page=1&limit=10&start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
